<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payout Request Received</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background: #f9fafb; }
        .container { background: white; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.07); }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0891b2, #0e7490); color: white; text-align: center; padding: 32px 24px; }
        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600; }
        .header .subtitle { margin: 8px 0 0 0; opacity: 0.95; font-size: 15px; }
        .content { padding: 32px 24px; }
        .greeting { font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #1e293b; }
        .amount-section { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7, #fde68a); border: 2px solid #fbbf24; border-radius: 10px; padding: 24px; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; }
        .amount { font-size: 38px; font-weight: 700; color: #92400e; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .status-badge { background: #fbbf24; color: #78350f; padding: 8px 18px; border-radius: 20px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
        .details-section { margin: 24px 0; }
        .details-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; margin: 16px 0; }
        .detail-box { background: #f8fafc; padding: 14px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #0891b2; }
        .detail-label { font-size: 11px; color: #64748b; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
        .detail-value { font-size: 15px; color: #0f172a; font-weight: 500; word-break: break-all; }
        .info-box { background: #dbeafe; border-left: 3px solid #3b82f6; padding: 16px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #1e40af; }
        .timeline-compact { background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .timeline-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #334155; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .timeline-item { display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 8px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #475569; }
        .timeline-icon { width: 20px; height: 20px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-right: 10px; font-size: 11px; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .icon-active { background: #16a34a; color: white; font-weight: 600; }
        .icon-pending { background: #e5e7eb; color: #6b7280; }
        .support-compact { background: #f0f9ff; border: 1px solid #bae6fd; border-radius: 6px; padding: 14px; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 13px; }
        .support-compact strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #0c4a6e; font-size: 14px; }
        .support-item { padding: 4px 0; color: #0369a1; }
        .button { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0891b2, #0e7490); color: white; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; margin: 24px 0 16px 0; box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(8,145,178,0.2); }
        .button:hover { opacity: 0.95; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 24px; background: #f9fafb; color: #64748b; font-size: 13px; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
        .footer a { color: #0891b2; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }
        @media (max-width: 480px) { .details-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .content { padding: 24px 20px; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üìã Payout Request Received</h1>
            <div class="subtitle">Now under review</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">Hi <strong>{{firstName}}</strong>,</div>
            
            <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; color: #475569; font-size: 15px;">We've received your payout request and it's now being reviewed by our finance team.</p>

            <div class="amount-section">
                <div class="amount">${{amount}}</div>
                <span class="status-badge">PENDING REVIEW</span>
            </div>

            <div class="details-section">
                <div class="details-grid">
                    <div class="detail-box">
                        <div class="detail-label">Payout ID</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{payoutId}}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-box">
                        <div class="detail-label">Agent Code</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{agentCode}}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-box">
                        <div class="detail-label">Payment Method</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{paymentMethod}}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-box">
                        <div class="detail-label">Request Date</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{requestDate}}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            {{#if description}}
            <div class="detail-box" style="border-left-color: #94a3b8;">
                <div class="detail-label">Description</div>
                <div class="detail-value">{{description}}</div>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <div class="info-box">
                <strong>üîç What's Next:</strong> Our finance team will review your request within 2-3 business days. You'll receive an email notification once approved.
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-compact">
                <div class="timeline-title">Review Process</div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-icon icon-active">‚úì</div>
                    <div><strong>Request Submitted</strong> - Received and queued</div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-icon icon-pending">2</div>
                    <div><strong>Under Review</strong> - Finance verification</div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-icon icon-pending">3</div>
                    <div><strong>Approved</strong> - Processing payment</div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-icon icon-pending">4</div>
                    <div><strong>Complete</strong> - Funds transferred</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center; padding: 16px; background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <p style="margin: 0; color: #475569; font-size: 14px;">
                    <strong>üì± Track Status:</strong> Login to your account at<br>
                    <a href="{{agentPortalUrl}}" style="color: #0891b2; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">portal.planettalk.com</a>
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="support-compact">
                <strong>üí¨ Need Help?</strong>
                <div class="support-item">üìß Email: <a href="mailto:agent@planettalk.com" style="color: #0891b2; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">agent@planettalk.com</a></div>
                <div class="support-item">üí¨ Live Chat: Available in your dashboard</div>
                <div class="support-item">üé´ Reference: {{payoutId}}</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0;"><strong>Thank you for being part of PlanetTalk!</strong></p>
            <p style="margin: 0;">Best regards, <strong>The PlanetTalk Team</strong></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
